HEADWORD: Antilithic
<hw>An`ti*lith"ic</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Med.)</fld>
<def>Tending to prevent the formation of urinary calculi, or to destroy
them when formed.</def> -- <def2><pos>n.</pos> <def>An antilithic
medicine.</def></def2>⟦br⟧
